ider.com%20(Joshua%20Nelken-Zitser)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-gaza-cease-fire-deal-biden-increasingly-likely-within-days-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Butt%20Of%20Jokes%20To%20Life%20Saver%3A%20The%20150-Year%20Evolution%20Of%20Weather%20Office%20IMD%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20weather%20office%2C%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20oldest%20scientific%20organisations%20and%20marked%20150%20years%20of%20its%20existence%20on%20Tuesday.%20While%20most%20are%20celebrating%20its%20successes%2C%20many%20still%20make%20fun%20of%20its%20predictions%20-%20a%20common%20joke%20goes%20that%20if%20the%20IMD%20predicts%20rainfall%2C%20please%20leave%20your%20umbrella%20at%20home.%20This%20is%20unfair%20to%20an%20organisation%20that%20helps%20forecast%20weather%20for%20a%20country%20as%20geographically%20diverse%20and%20as%20big%20as%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20compare%20the%20forecasts%20issued%20for%20cities%20like%20New%20York%2C%20Washington%20DC%2C%20London%20or%20Paris%20and%20suggest%20that%20weather%20offices%20there%20are%20able%20to%20give%20accurate%20forecasts%2C%20while%20the%20IMD%20fumbles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20western%20cities%20we%20compare%20the%20forecasts%20with%20all%20fall%20in%20the%20temperate%20zone%2C%20where%20the%20weather%20is%20fairly%20stable%20and%20predictable.%20In%20comparison%2C%20India%20is%20a%20tropical%20country%20and%20the%20prevailing%20atmospheric%20conditions%20are%20best%20described%20as%20'chaotic'.%20Scientifically%2C%20'chaos'%20is%20best%20defined%20as%20a%20'deterministic%20system%20that's%20difficult%20to%20predict%20because%20it%20is%20sensitive%20to%20small%20changes%20in%20initial%20conditions'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20tropical%20conditions%2C%20making%20forecasts%20is%20very%20difficult%20and%20that%20has%20to%20do%20with%20the%20inherent%20lack%20of%20understanding%20of%20the%20science%20of%20'chaos'.%20Given%20these%20conditions%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20IMD%20makes%20accountable%20forecasts%20is%20very%20creditable%2C%20and%20that%20they%20are%20improving%20is%20even%20better.%20Today%2C%20IMD's%20three-day%20forecasts%20and%20nowcasts%2C%20all%20called%20short-term%20forecasts%2C%20are%20becoming%20very%20accurate.%20It%20is%20the%20medium-term%20and%20long-range%20forecasts%20where%20improvements%20will%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20150th%20Foundation%20Day%20celebrations%20of%20the%20IMD%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20lauded%20this%20short-term%20forecast%20and%20said%20he%20was%20a%20big%20beneficiary%2C%20highlighting%20that%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Z-Morh%20or%20Sonmarg%20Tunnel%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Ganderbal%20was%20scheduled%20for%20Monday%20after%20consulting%20the%20local%20weather%20office%20and%20that%20he%20was%20blessed%20with%20sunshine%20as%20predicted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECyclone%20Prediction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20area%20where%20the%20IMD%20has%20done%20incredibly%20well%20is%20in%20forecasting%20and%20tracking%20cyclones.%20Today%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20use%20of%20satellite%20data%20and%20Doppler%20radars%2C%20the%20tracking%20of%20cyclones%20can%20be%20done%20with%20almost%20pinpoint%20precision.%20Before%20Indian%20weather%20satellites%20became%20operational%2C%20cyclones%20like%20the%20one%20which%20hit%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20in%201970%20killed%20300%2C000%20people.%20Today%2C%20cyclones%20are%20tracked%20days%20in%20advance%20and%20the%20number%20of%20deaths%20has%20dropped%20to%20double%20digits%20or%20even%20none.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20IMD%20event%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20PM%20Modi%20highlighted%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bintegration%20of%20science%20and%20preparedness%20has%20also%20reduced%20economic%20losses%20worth%20billions%20of%20rupees%2C%20creating%20resilience%20in%20the%20economy%20and%20boosting%20investor%20confidence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForecasting%20cyclones%20is%20indeed%20a%20huge%20achievement%20and%20some%20of%20the%20credit%20should%20go%20to%20India's%20'cyclone%20forecasting%20hero'%2C%20Dr%20Mrutyunjay%20Mohapatra%2C%20the%20current%20head%20of%20the%20IMD%2C%20who%20is%20a%20specialist%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMonsoon%20And%20Droughts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20place%20where%20the%20IMD%20needs%20to%20improve%20is%20long-range%20accurate%20forecasting%20of%20the%20Monsoon.%20This%20is%20critical%20for%20India%20as%20much%20of%20the%20rainfall%20in%20the%20country%20occurs%20in%20the%20June-to-September%20period%2C%20during%20the%20southwest%20Monsoon%20season.%20Forecasting%20the%20Monsoon%20is%20tough%20because%20the%20science%20behind%20doing%20so%20is%20still%20not%20well%20understood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20invested%20almost%20Rs%20300%20crore%20in%20the%20Monsoon%20Mission%20and%20upgraded%20supercomputers%2C%20but%20precision%20in%20this%20area%20eludes%20India's%20weather%20office.%20The%20IMD%20gets%20criticised%20for%20this%20lack%20of%20precision%2C%20but%20the%20basics%20of%20this%20phenomenon%2C%20which%20depends%20on%20ocean-atmosphere%20interactions%2C%20elude%20global%20scientists%20too.%20On%20top%20of%20this%2C%20climate%20change%20is%20playing%20havoc%20with%20existing%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPredicting%20a%20normal%20monsoon%20is%20the%20easiest%20as%2C%20statistically%2C%20doing%20so%20is%20better%20than%20predicting%20heads%20or%20tails%20on%20a%20flip%20of%20a%20coin.%20The%20greatest%20need%20is%20to%20be%20able%20to%20predict%20a%20drought%20early%20in%20the%20season%20and%20this%20requires%20deeper%20knowledge.%20Even%20now%2C%20despite%20massive%20computers%20and%20big%20data%2C%20it%20is%20the%20human%20skill%20of%20the%20weatherman%20which%20plays%20a%20big%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHopefully%2C%20the%20Rs%202%2C000-crore%20Mission%20Mausam%20inaugurated%20on%20Tuesday%20by%20PM%20Modi%20will%20help%20in%20deciphering%20the%20many%20unsolved%20mysteries%20of%20the%20Monsoon.%20Maybe%20the%20time%20has%20come%20to%20call%20a%20moratorium%20on%20long-range%20forecasting%20of%20the%20monsoon%20at%20least%20till%20such%20time%20as%20our%20scientists%20can%20better%20understand%20the%20underlying%20physics%2C%20chemistry%20and%20dynamics%20of%20what%20drives%20and%20sustains%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeather%20plays%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20the%20everyday%20lives%20of%20citizens%20and%2C%20today%2C%20the%20need%20is%20to%20be%20'weather%20ready%20and%20climate-smart'.%20Or%2C%20as%20India's%20science%20minister%20Dr%20Jitendra%20Singh%20aptly%20put%20it%2C%20'Today%2C%20it%20is%20not%20what%20the%20weather%20will%20be%20tomorrow%20but%20what%20weather%20will%20do%20tomorrow'.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736855220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F1df75s5o_weather-generic_625x300_14_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-butt-of-jokes-to-life-saver-the-150-year-evolution-of-weather-office-imd-7471763%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20weather%20office%2C%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20oldest%20scientific%20organisations%20and%20marked%20150%20years%20of%20its%20existence%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-butt-of-jokes-to-life-saver-the-150-year-evolution-of-weather-office-imd-7471763%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Deal%20for%20307%20'Made%20in%20India'%20ATAGS%20guns%20likely%20by%20March%3A%20Indian%20Army%20Chief%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736855192000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fex