ored%20a%20mega-round%20of%20funding%20for%20its%20AI%20that%20gets%20patients%20ready%20for%20the%20operating%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQventus%20has%20raised%20%24105%20million%20in%20Series%20D%20funding%20led%20by%20private%20equity%20giant%20KKR%2C%20the%20startup%20announced%20Monday.%20Three%20of%20Qventus's%20health%20system%20customers%2C%20Northwestern%20Medicine%2C%20HonorHealth%2C%20and%20Allina%20Health%2C%20joined%20the%20round%2C%20along%20with%20previous%20Qventus%20investor%20Bessemer%20Venture%20Partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20funding%20comes%20as%20Qventus%20ramps%20up%20its%20new%20AI-powered%20assistant%20tech%2C%20built%20in%20partnership%20with%20Northwestern%20Medicine%20and%20other%20health%20systems.%20The%20startup's%20software%2C%20launched%20in%20August%2C%20aims%20to%20automate%20a%20range%20of%20non-clinical%20tasks%20before%20and%20after%20surgery%2C%20including%20messaging%20with%20patients%2C%20making%20phone%20calls%20to%20other%20healthcare%20organizations%20to%20retrieve%20a%20patient's%20medical%20records%2C%20and%20sending%20and%20receiving%20faxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQventus%20has%20spent%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20building%20technology%20to%20automate%20hospital%20operations%20such%20as%20surgical%20scheduling.%20Founded%20in%202012%2C%20it's%20raised%20%24200%20million%20to%20date%20from%20investors%20including%20Bessemer%20Venture%20Partners%2C%20Norwest%20Venture%20Partners%2C%20and%20Mayfield%20Fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20AI%20assistant%20tech%20is%20supercharging%20Qventus's%20growth%2C%20CEO%20Mudit%20Garg%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey've%20had%20the%20fastest%20uptake%20of%20anything%20we've%20built%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years%20and%20very%20high%20resonance%20with%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20Garg%20said%20of%20the%20operational%20assistants.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20accelerating%20the%20whole%20process%20and%20the%20speed%20at%20which%20we%20bring%20new%20solutions%20to%20market.%26quot%