r.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20had%20taken%20a%20break%20from%20movies%20and%20is%20returning%20to%20the%20screen%20about%20two%20decades%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rao's%20remarks%20were%20widely%20criticised%2C%20with%20social%20media%20users%20describing%20them%20as%20%26quot%3Bcheap%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3Bsexist%26quot%3B%20and%20in%20poor%20taste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20controversy%2C%20Mr%20Rao%20released%20a%20video%20and%20apologised%20for%20the%20remarks.%20%26quot%3BMy%20comments%20in%20the%20Mazaka%20teaser%20release%20were%20not%20intentional%2C%20and%20I%20only%20did%20it%20to%20make%20everyone%20laugh.%20But%20because%20several%20women%20are%20hurt%2C%20I%20apologise%20unconditionally%20for%20those%20comments%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20Anshu%20backed%20Mr%20Rao%20and%20said%20his%20words%20may%20have%20been%20taken%20out%20of%20context.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20there%20were%20some%20stories%20out%20with%20regard%20to%20Trinath%20Garu's%20comments.%20I%20really%20want%20to%20assure%20you%20all%20that%20he%20is%20the%20loveliest%20man%20on%20the%20planet%2C%20he%20really%20is%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20his%20words%20may%20have%20been%20taken%20out%20of%20context.%20He%20has%20treated%20me%20as%20a%20member%20of%20his%20family.%20I%20have%20worked%20on%20this%20movie%20for%2060%20days%20and%20I%20have%20been%20given%20nothing%20but%20respect%2C%20love%20and%20lots%20of%20good%20wishes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20please%20everybody%2C%20we%20can%20put%20this%20to%20bed%20because%20I%20am%20so%20excited%20for%20the%20movie%20and%20I%20feel%20we%20should%20all%20watch%20the%20film%20for%20the%20right%20reasons.%20Trinath%20sir%20has%20been%20an%20absolute%20pleasure%20to%20work%20with.%20I%20could%20not%20have%20asked%20for%20a%20better%20director%20to%20bring%20me%20back%20to%20the%20Telugu%20film%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20video%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2