on%20to%20Porto%20in%20order%20to%20protect%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20aircraft%2C%20160%20passengers%20and%206%20crew%20members%20on%20board%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20from%20the%20European%20budget%20airlines%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fryanair-drunk-passengers-rowdy-limit-alcohol-sales-airport-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736851227000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6786374e50dfd88e193e2f63%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fryanair-drunk-passengers-rowdy-limit-alcohol-sales-airport-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20fail%20to%20understand%20why%20passengers%20at%20airports%20are%20not%20limited%20to%202%20alcoholic%20drinks%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryanair%2C%20Europe's%20biggest%20airline%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nredmond%40insider.com%20(Nora%20Redmond)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fryanair-drunk-passengers-rowdy-limit-alcohol-sales-airport-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Musk%20Is%20Becoming%20A%20Menace%20For%20Europe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20opposition%20is%20so%20invisible%20these%20days%20you%20might%20be%20forgiven%20for%20thinking%20it%20hardly%20exists.%20Labour%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%20seems%20to%20have%20no%20one%20capable%20of%20holding%20his%20government%20to%20account.%20After%20last%20year's%20electoral%20thrashing%2C%20the%20Conservatives%20are%20a%20shipwreck%20without%20a%20captain%E2%80%94rudderless%2C%20clueless%20and%20still%20hungover%20from%20their%2014-year%20binge%20on%20power.%20They%20do%20not%20appear%20to%20be%20sobering%20up%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20Starmer%20isn't%20exactly%20sleeping%20easy.%20Because%2C%20the%20vacuum%20left%20by%20Britain's%20hapless%20opposition%20has%20been%20enthusiastically%20filled%20by%20none%20other%20than%20the%20world's%20richest%20man%2C%20Elon%20Musk.%20Stepping%20in%20with%20a%20storm%20of%20tweets%E2%80%94%20or%2C%20should%20we%20say%2C%20an%20X-avalanche%E2%80%94on%20New%20Year's%20Day%2C%20Musk%20called%20for%20the%20King%20to%20dissolve%20Starmer's%20government%20and%20hold%20a%20fresh%20election.%20Then%2C%20for%20good%20measure%2C%20he%20accused%20Starmer%20of%20failing%20to%20prosecute%20grooming%20gangs%20and%20demanded%20that%20safeguarding%20minister%20Jess%20Phillips%20be%20locked%20up.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStarmer%20Gets%20An%20Opposition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20looks%20like%20the%20opposition%20Starmer%20never%20asked%20for%20has%20arrived%2C%20with%20a%20tech%20billionaire's%20signature%20flair%20for%20political%20drama%20and%2C%20surely%2C%20a%20strong%20hint%20of%20disrupting%20British%20politics.%20Starmer%20responded%20to%20Musk's%20accusation%20against%20him%20that%20he%20had%20ignored%20child%20exploitation%20cases%20as%20chief%20prosecutor%20between%202008-13.%20Musk%20also%20stirred%20up%20interest%20in%20far-right%20activist%20Tommy%20Robinson%2C%20calling%20for%20his%20release%20despite%20the%20latter's%20criminal%20record%20and%20controversial%20past.%20Currently%2C%20he%20is%20serving%20an%2018-month%20jail%20term%20for%20defamation%20and%20being%20kept%20in%20solitary%20confinement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk's%20posts%20have%20shifted%20public%20focus%2C%20sidelining%20the%20UK%20government's%20priorities%2C%20such%20as%20the%20NHS%20reforms.%20No%20doubt%20the%20Tesla%20owner%20seems%20fixated%20on%20UK%20politics.%20Musk%20had%20already%20declared%20the%20new%20British%20government%20his%20enemy%20last%20summer%20after%20riots%20broke%20out%20following%20fatal%20stabbings%20of%20children%20in%20Southport.%20Back%20then%2C%20he%20claimed%20%E2%80%9Ccivil%20war%20was%20inevitable%E2%80%9D%20in%20Britain%20and%20nicknamed%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20%E2%80%9CTwoTierKeir%E2%80%9D%2C%20referring%20to%20a%20far-right%20conspiracy%20theory%20about%20unequal%20policing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20latest%20comments%20have%20sparked%20serious%20controversy%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20with%20Health%20Secretary%20(minister)%20Wes%20Streeting%20dismissing%20them%20as%20%26quot%3Bmisjudged%20and%20misinformed%26quot%3B.%20Streeting%20emphasised%20Starmer's%20reforms%20in%202013%20to%20improve%20prosecution%20standards%20for%20child%20abuse%20cases.%20The%20British%20media%20appears%20to%20be%20defending%20their%20prime%20minister.%20One%20columnist%20called%20Musk%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20South%20African%20anarchic%20tech-futurist%26quot%3B%2C%20referring%20to%20his%20South%20African%20origin.%20Starmer%2C%20too%2C%20hit%20back%20at%20Musk%20and%20without%20naming%20him%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthose%20that%20are%20spreading%20lies%20and%20misinformation%20as%20far%20and%20wide%20as%20possible%2C%20they're%20not%20interested%20in%20victims.%20They're%20interested%20in%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Office%20is%20reportedly%20keeping%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20Elon%20Musk's%20social%20media%20activity%20to%20assess%20its%20reach%2C%20influence%20and%20potential%20harm.%20According%20to%20British%20media%2C%20this%20monitoring%20aims%20to%20stay%20ahead%20of%20any%20challenges%20posed%20by%20%26quot%3Bnon-state%20actors%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'Grooming%20Gangs'%20Controversy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scrutiny%20of%20Musk's%20posts%20began%20after%20his%20controversial%20comments%20about%20safeguarding%20Minister%20Jess%20Phillips.%20The%20US%20tech%20billionaire%20labelled%20her%20a%20%26quot%3Brape%20genocide%20apologist%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20for%20her%20imprisonment.%20Phillips%2C%20a%20long-time%20advocate%20against%20violence%20towards%20women%20who%20previously%20ran%20a%20domestic%20abuse%20refuge%2C%20revealed%20that%20Musk's%20remarks%20have%20led%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20threats%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%2C%20Musk%20demands%20a%20new%20public%20inquiry%20and%20immediate%20elections.%20The%20grooming%20gangs%20inquiry%20is%20an%20uncomfortable%20thorn%20in%20the%20government's%20side.%20Musk%2C%20ever%20the%20provocateur%2C%20has%20merely%20echoed%20what%20critics%20of%20the%20British%20establishment%20have%20been%20saying%3A%20why%20hasn't%20a%20fresh%20national%20inquiry%20into%20these%20networks%20been%20launched%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFair%20question%E2%80%94critics%20have%20every%20right%20to%20demand%20answers%20about%20why%20systemic%20child%20exploitation%2C%20ignored%20by%20layers%20of%20police%20forces%2C%20councils%20and%20the%20Conservative%20government%20for%2014%20years%20until%20the%202024%20election%2C%20hasn't%20been%20properly%20addressed.%20But%20wait%20a%20second.%20None%20other%20than%20Conservative%20leader%20Kemi%20Badenoch%2C%20suddenly%20a%20champion%20of%20justice%20now%2C%20is%20calling%20for%20a%20fresh%20national%20inquiry%2C%20conveniently%20after%20Musk's%20intervention.%20She%20claims%20%E2%80%9Cno%20one%20in%20authority%20has%20joined%20the%20dots%E2%80%9D.%20Really%3F%20Someone%20might%20want%20to%20remind%20her%20that%20she%20and%20her%20party%20had%20a%20whole%2014%20years%20in%20power%20to%20%E2%80%9Cjoin%20the%20dots%E2%80%9D.%20What%20stopped%20them%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20Musk%20has%20raised%20is%20serious%E2%80%94child%20abuse%20by%20grooming%20gangs%20is%20far%20too%20important%20to%20be%20treated%20as%20a%20billionaire's%20personal%20hobby.%20It%20has%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20significant%20scrutiny%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20with%20numerous%20investigations%20at%20national%20and%20local%20levels%20shedding%20light%20on%20systemic%20failures%20and%20patterns%20of%20abuse.%20But%20I%20support%20a%20full%20and%20thorough%2C%20countrywide%20inquiry%20because%20I%20believe%20the%20gangs%20still%20exist%20and%20the%20authorities%20are%20still%20failing%20in%20their%20duty%20to%20bust%20them%20and%20protect%20young%20girls.%20Here%20is%20a%20snapshot%20of%20inquiries%20that%20have%20happened%20so%20far%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Jay%20Report%20(2014)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Commissioned%20by%20Rotherham%20Council%2C%20this%20report%20revealed%20the%20horrifying%20sexual%20exploitation%20of%20over%201%2C400%20children%20in%20Rotherham%20between%201997%20and%202013%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndependent%20Inquiry%20into%20Child%20Sexual%20Abuse%20(2014%E2%80%932022)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20broader%20investigation%20examined%20institutional%20failings%20across%20England%20and%20Wales%2C%20including%20responses%20to%20grooming%20gangs.%20It%20highlighted%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20credible%20database%20and%20inconclusive%20facts%20but%20confirmed%20the%20issue%20extended%20beyond%20Northern%20towns%20to%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ELocal%20Investigations%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Councils%20in%20towns%20such%20as%20Rochdale%2C%20Oxford%2C%20and%20Newcastle%20commissioned%20their%20own%20reports%20following%20high-profile%20cases.%20These%20investigations%20exposed%20repeated%20systemic%20failures%20by%20police%20and%20social%20services%20in%20addressing%20grooming%20and%20exploitation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20perception%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20grooming%20gang%20offenders%20are%20of%20Pakistani%20origin%20(often%20from%20Mirpur%20in%20POK)%20stems%20from%20cases%20in%20regions%20like%20Rotherham%2C%20Rochdale%2C%20and%20Telford.%20However%2C%20official%20findings%20complicate%20this%20narrative.%20A%202020%20review%20of%20offender%20characteristics%20by%20the%20Home%20Office%20Research%20found%20that%20offenders%20came%20from%20diverse%20ethnic%20backgrounds%2C%20with%20the%20majority%20being%20white%20men%2C%20consistent%20with%20the%20UK's%20demographic%20makeup.%20The%20report%20emphasised%20that%20there%20was%20no%20reliable%20evidence%20to%20suggest%20that%20grooming%20was%20unique%20to%20any%20one%20ethnic%20group.%20%C2%A0Also%2C%20while%20many%20offenders%20in%20high-profile%20cases%20in%20the%20north%20of%20the%20country%20were%20of%20Pakistani%20descent%2C%20others%20included%20white%20offenders%20and%20even%20some%20white%20women%20who%20reportedly%20lured%20victims%20for%20these%20gangs.%20Convictions%20related%20to%20grooming%20gangs%20have%20occurred%20across%20the%20UK%2C%20including%20in%20towns%20such%20as%20Rochdale%2C%20Rotherham%2C%20Oxford%20and%20Newcastle.%20Convictions%20have%20included%20individuals%20from%20various%20ethnic%20backgrounds.%20What%20many%20observers%20say%20is%20that%20the%20grooming%20gangs%20of%20Pakistani%20origin%20are%20mostly%20organised%20and%20work%20in%20tandem%2C%20whereas%20offenders%20from%20other%20communities%20work%20solo.%20Across%20investigations%2C%20what%20has%20remained%20common%20is%20a%20systemic%20failure%20of%20authorities%20to%20investigate%20the%20cases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMusk%20Is%20Europe's%20Menace%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFresh%20off%20leveraging%20his%20platform%20X%20and%20enjoying%20cosy%20ties%20with%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20Musk%20is%20now%20bringing%20his%20unique%20brand%20of%20an%20influencer%20of%20sorts%20to%20the%20Atlantic.%20From%20backing%20Germany's%20far-right%20AfD%20to%20taking%20swipes%20at%20UK%20leaders%2C%20he%20is%20sparking%20debates%20about%20democracy%2C%20accountability%20and%20the%20unchecked%20influence%20of%20tech%20titans.%20On%20January%209%2C%20he%20hosted%20a%20live%20%26quot%3BSpaces%26quot%3B%20chat%20with%20Alice%20Weidel%2C%20co-leader%20of%20Germany's%20Alternative%20for%20Germany%20(AfD)%20and%20their%20chancellor%20candidate.%20With%20German%20elections%20due%20on%20February%2023%2C%20this%20move%20is%20widely%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20sway%20the%20political%20tide.%20The%20AfD%2C%20polling%20around%2020%25%2C%20has%20climbed%20to%20second%20place%20but%20remains%20an%20untouchable%20player%20for%20Germany's%20mainstream%20parties%2C%20which%20refuse%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20it.%20Though%20that%20hasn't%20stopped%20Musk%20from%20cosying%20up%20to%20the%20AfD%2C%20despite%20its%20anti-immigration%20rhetoric%20and%20EU%20scepticism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk's%20political%20mischief%20isn't%20confined%20to%20Germany%20or%20the%20UK.%20He's%20been%20rubbing%20shoulders%20with%20other%20European%20far-right%20figures%2C%20including%20Italy's%20Prime%20Minister%20Giorgia%20Meloni%2C%20raising%20eyebrows%20among%20Europe's%20left-of-centre%20leaders.%20Critics%20worry%20his%20growing%20influence%20is%20less%20about%20defending%20democracy%20and%20more%20about%20destabilising%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Threat%20To%20Electoral%20Integrity%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20insists%20his%20actions%20are%20a%20noble%20exercise%20of%20free%20speech%2C%20but%20his%20critics%20aren't%20buying%20it.%20They%20accuse%20him%20of%20using%20X%20to%20amplify%20far-right%20narratives%2C%20drowning%20out%20dissenting%20voices.%20These%20claims%20are%20now%20under%20investigation%20by%20the%20European%20Commission%20under%20the%20Digital%20Services%20Act%20(DSA).%20If%20Musk's%20meddling%20breaches%20the%20DSA%2C%20his%20platform%20could%20face%20hefty%20fines%E2%80%94or%20even%20a%20ban%20in%20the%20EU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELate%20last%20year%2C%20Musk%20even%20took%20aim%20at%20German%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%2C%20calling%20him%20a%20%E2%80%9Cfool%E2%80%9D%20(%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EOlaf%20ist%20ein%20Narr%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D)%20in%20a%20post%20that%20added%20fuel%20to%20an%20already%20fiery%20political%20discourse.%20Scholz%20and%20Green%20Party%20candidate%20Robert%20Habeck%20have%20openly%20criticised%20Musk's%20interference%2C%20with%20Scholz%20warning%20against%20external%20threats%20to%20German%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComplicating%20matters%20further%2C%20Musk's%20new%20role%20in%20the%20US%20under%20President%20Trump%2C%20as%20co-chair%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%2C%20makes%20his%20foreign%20political%20statements%20look%20a%20lot%20like%20extensions%20of%20US%20policy.%20Is%20Musk%20playing%20disruptor-in-chief%20for%20his%20own%20gain%2C%20or%20as%20a%20de%20facto%20envoy%20for%20Trump's%20administration%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20The%20Onslaught%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20frames%20his%20actions%20as%20a%20crusade%20against%20the%20%E2%80%9Cwoke%20mind%20virus%E2%80%9D%20and%20centralised%20authority%2C%20but%20critics%20argue%20it's%20more%20about%20power%20and%20profit.%20Germany%2C%20home%20to%20one%20of%20Tesla's%20largest%20factories%2C%20might%20just%20be%20another%20pawn%20in%20Musk's%20chessboard%20of%20business%20interests.%20Similarly%2C%20his%20attacks%20on%20UK%20leaders%20conveniently%20align%20with%20debates%20over%20tech%20regulations%20that%20could%20impact%20his%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20critics%20say%20that%20Musk's%20interventions%E2%80%94something%20he%20brands%20as%20%E2%80%98free%20speech'%E2%80%94go%20beyond%20sparking%20debate%20and%20instead%20deepen%20divisions%2C%20empower%20extremists%20and%20fuel%20a%20breeding%20ground%20for%20misinformation.%20By%20dominating%20political%20discourse%2C%20he%20keeps%20himself%E2%80%94and%20his%20platforms%E2%80%94at%20the%20centre%20of%20global%20conversations%2C%20no%20matter%20the%20cost%20to%20Europe's%20fragile%20political%20balance.%20%C2%A0The%20question%20for%20Europe%20now%20is%2C%20how%20much%20influence%20are%20they%20willing%20to%20cede%20to%20a%20tech%20billionaire%20with%20a%20penchant%20for%20stirring%20the%20pot%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3ESyed%20Zubair%20Ahmed%20is%20a%20London-based%20senior%20Indian%20journalist%20with%20three%20decades%20of%20experience%20with%20the%20Western%20medi