%2C%20subsequently%2C%20notified%20the%20police%20and%20an%20investigation%20is%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SIT%20had%20been%20formed%20to%20conduct%20a%20comprehensive%20probe%20into%20the%20incident%2C%20with%20Pathanamthitta%20Deputy%20SP%20P%20S%20Nandakumar%20leading%20the%20team%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20District%20Police%20Chief%20V%20G%20Vinod%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20comprises%20over%2030%20police%20officers%2C%20including%20women%2C%20from%20various%20ranks%20and%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDIG%20Ajitha%20Beegam%20said%20that%20once%20the%20Sabarimala%20pilgrimage%20season%20gets%20over%2C%20more%20officers%20will%20be%20included%20in%20the%20SIT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736850420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-11%2Fot9qoiqo_kerala-police-van_625x300_03_November_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F44-arrested-after-dalit-teen-alleges-rape-for-over-5-years-in-kerala-7471232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20of%20Kerala%20police%20probing%20the%20sensational%20case%20of%20alleged%20sexual%20abuse%20of%20a%20Dalit%20girl%20in%20the%20district%20has%20arrested%2044%20people%20so%20far%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20matter%2C%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%20of%20the%20district%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F44-arrested-after-dalit-teen-alleges-rape-for-over-5-years-in-kerala-7471232%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22EU%20continues%20to%20savour%20Russian%20LNG%20as%20US%20sanctions%20threaten%20India's%20imports%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736850265000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%