0about%20AI%20and%20get%20better%20stories%20about%20the%20technology.%20He%20was%20right.%20There's%20a%20lot%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-peak-data-google-deepmind-researchers-solution-test-time-compute-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Evaluable%20information%20%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3Eburied%20in%20these%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJack%20stayed%20at%20OpenAI%20for%20over%20four%20years%2C%20doing%20strategy%20and%20communications%20before%20becoming%20a%20policy%20director.%20He%20may%20have%20gotten%20some%20equity%20in%20that%20startup%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20sure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20in%202020%2C%20he%20left%20OpenAI%20and%20I%20didn't%20hear%20from%20him%20for%20a%20while.%20He%20popped%20up%20a%20few%20months%20later%20as%20one%20of%20seven%20cofounders%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-gaining-on-openai-ai-market-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20started%20by%20a%20bunch%20of%20early%20OpenAI%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226beb63f4-5df7-487a-bfc9-9d2033d0711f%5C%22%3ECofounders%20reminisce%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20is%20now%20challenging%20OpenAI%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20generative%20AI%20and%20large%20language%20models.%20It's%20backed%20by%20Amazon%20and%20Google%2C%20along%20with%20several%20top%20venture%20capital%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cofounders%20got%20together%20last%20month%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20start%20of%20Anthropic.%20Jack%20holds%20court%20with%20his%20colleagues%2C%20who%20reminisce%20about%20the%20early%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fom2lIWXLLN4%3Ffeature%3Doem