2originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fvaranasi%2Fnursing-college-principal-commits-suicide-by-jumping-in-front-of-train-in-varanasi%2Farticleshow%2F117233039.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sushmita%20Singh%2C%20the%20principal%20of%20a%20nursing%20college%20in%20Varanasi%2C%20ended%20her%20life%20by%20jumping%20in%20front%20of%20a%20train.%20The%20incident%20occurred%20near%20the%20Tarna%20overbridge.%20The%20police%20are%20investigating%20her%20mobile%20data%20to%20understand%20the%20reasons%20behind%20her%20suicide.%20Her%20body%20has%20been%20sent%20for%20post-mortem.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TNN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fvaranasi%2Fnursing-college-principal-commits-suicide-by-jumping-in-front-of-train-in-varanasi%2Farticleshow%2F117233039.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RBI%20Governor%20Signals%20He's%20Open%20To%20More%20Flexible%20Rupee%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENew%20central%20bank%20governor%20has%20shown%20a%20willingness%20to%20allow%20the%20rupee%20to%20move%20more%20freely%20in%20tandem%20with%20peers%20in%20the%20region%20while%20still%20intervening%20in%20the%20foreign-exchange%20market%20to%20curb%20excessive%20moves%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20regulator's%20thinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20Governor%20Sanjay%20Malhotra%2C%20who%20took%20office%20in%20December%2C%20has%20held%20multiple%20meetings%20with%20departments%20at%20the%20central%20bank%20ahead%20of%20his%20first%20monetary%20policy%20meeting%20in%20February%2C%20the%20people%20said%2C%20asking%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20as%20the%20discussions%20are%20private.%20He's%20showed%20keen%20interest%20in%20the%20RBI's%20currency%20intervention%20functions%20and%20expressed%20no%20opposition%20when%20his%20team%20explained%20the%20recent%20movements%20in%20the%20rupee%20and%20the%20need%20to%20allow%20it%20to%20depreciate%2C%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI's%20overall%20objective%20is%20still%20to%20avoid%20targeting%20a%20specific%20level%20for%20the%20rupee%20and%20to%20intervene%20regularly%20to%20curb%20excessive%20volatility%20and%20prevent%20any%20speculative%20attacks%2C%20the%20people%20said.%20The%20new%20governor%20may%20allow%20a%20wider%20gap%20in%20the%20closing%20level%20of%20the%20currency%20from%20the%20previous%20day's%20close%20if%20the%20situation%20warrants%2C%20the%20people%20said%2C%20without%20providing%20more%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20signals%20from%20the%20new%20governor%20suggest%20a%20departure%20from%20his%20predecessor%2C%20Shaktikanta%20Das%2C%20who%20kept%20a%20tight%20rein%20on%20the%20currency.%20Under%20Mr%20Das's%20six%20years%20at%20the%20RBI%2C%20the%20rupee's%20volatility%20slid%20to%20the%20lowest%20among%20emerging%20markets%2C%20second%20only%20to%20the%20pegged%20Hong%20Kong%20dollar.%20The%20RBI%20under%20Mr%20Das%20built%20up%20the%20world's%20fourth-biggest%20foreign%20exchange%20reserves%20of%20more%20than%20%24700%20billion%20and%20then%20used%20it%20to%20defend%20the%20currency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20an%20email%20seeking%20further%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fhobtstd_rupee-dollar-gfx-bloomberg_625x300_14_January_25.jpeg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rupee%20weakened%20sharply%20after%20the%20Bloomberg%20News%20report%2C%20losing%20as%20much%20as%200.14%25%20to%20touch%20a%20new%20record%20low%20of%2086.7025%20per%20dollar.%20It%20recouped%20losses%20soon%20after%20to%20trade%20at%2086.5875%20per%20dollar%20as%20of%202%3A28%20p.m.%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Mr%20Das's%20departure%2C%20the%20rupee%20has%20slumped%202%25%20against%20the%20dollar%20with%20the%20one-month%20implied%20volatility%20jumping%20to%20its%20highest%20in%20more%20than%20a%20year.%20The%20currency%20tumbled%20by%20the%20most%20in%20nearly%20two%20years%20Monday%20to%20cross%20the%20symbolic%2086%20a%20dollar%20level%2C%20fueled%20by%20a%20strong%20US%20currency%20and%20rising%20oil%20prices%20after%20sweeping%20sanctions%20on%20Russian%20energy.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rupee%20was%20among%20the%20better%20performers%20in%20Asia%20last%20year%2C%20falling%202.8%25%20against%20the%20dollar.%20The%20RBI's%20tight%20grip%20over%20the%20currency%20has%20meant%20that%20the%20currency's%20real%20effective%20exchange%20rate%2C%20or%20inflation-adjusted%20trade%20competitiveness%2C%20against%20its%20peers%20has%20risen%20to%20a%20record.%20The%2040-country%20trade-weighted%20gauge%20stood%20at%20a%20historic%20high%20of%20108.14%20in%20November%2C%20suggesting%20an%20overvaluation%20of%20about%208%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20is%20keeping%20a%20close%20watch%20on%20the%20real%20effective%20exchange%20rate%2C%20the%20people%20said%2C%20with%20November's%20overvaluation%20seen%20as%20excessive.%20The%20depreciation%20in%20the%20rupee%20corrects%20some%20of%20the%20overvaluation%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20portfolio%20outflows%20-%20foreign%20investors%20pulled%20out%20about%20%242%20billion%20from%20local%20shares%20so%20far%20this%20year%20and%20sold%20a%20net%20%24705.5%20million%20of%20fixed-income%20securities%20on%20Jan.%208%20-%20showed%20a%20stable%20exchange%20rate%20regime%20wasn't%20sufficient%20to%20retain%20investors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExporters%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20had%20raised%20concerns%20with%20the%20RBI%20last%20year%20on%20how%20the%20rupee's%20stability%20was%20hurting%20them%20when%20rival%20countries%20let%20their%20currencies%20depreciate.%20The%20RBI's%20policy%20on%20this%20already%20started%20changing%20during%20the%20end%20of%20Mr%20Das's%20tenure%2C%20and%20now%20there's%20a%20greater%20realization%20that%20the%20rupee%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20find%20its%20level%20more%20freely%20while%20keeping%20a%20close%20watch%20on%20speculative%20positions%2C%20the%20people%20said.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20central%20bank%20will%20allow%20greater%20depreciation%20in%20the%20rupee%2C%20it's%20also%20keenly%20aware%20of%20India's%20rising%20import%20bill%2C%20they%20said.%20Asia's%20third-largest%20economy%20imports%20nearly%2090%25%20of%20its%20oil%20and%20a%20weaker%20rupee%20has%20pushed%20up%20the%20country's%20energy%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20is%20keeping%20a%20close%20watch%20on%20open%20positions%2C%20the%20person%20said%2C%20and%20won't%20hesitate%20to%20intervene%20significantly%20and%20suddenly%20to%20break%20a%20speculative%20build-up.%20The%20central%20bank%20also%20expects%20the%20rupee%20to%20strengthen%20somewhat%20after%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20sworn%20in%20as%20US%20president%20next%20week%20and%20sees%20some%20stability%20in%20the%20exchange%20rate%20by%20the%20time%20of%20the%20monetary%20policy%20meeting%20next%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736847660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F3bc3eg8g_rbi-governor-sanjay-malhotra-bloomberg_625x300_14_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Frbi-governor-sanjay-malhotra-signals-hes-open-to-more-flexible-rupee-7470917%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%20central%20bank%20governor%20has%20shown%20a%20willingness%20to%20allow%20the%20rupee%20to%20move%20more%20freely%20in%20tandem%20with%20peers%20in%20the%20region%20while%20still%20intervening%20in%20the%20foreign-exchange%20market%20to%20curb%20excessive%20moves%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https