%20'shivir'.%20She%20has%20some%20allergies.%20She%20has%20never%20been%20to%20such%20a%20crowded%20place.%20She%20is%20quite%20simple.%20She%20stayed%20with%20us%20during%20the%20pooja.%20Our%20tradition%20is%20such%20that%20those%20who%20have%20never%20seen%20it%20-%20they%20all%20want%20to%20join%2C%26quot%3B%20Giri%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Jobs%20arrived%20in%20Prayagraj%20on%20Monday%20to%20attend%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%2C%20which%20marks%20a%20rare%20celestial%20event%20in%20144%20years.%20Named%20'Kamala%20'%20by%20Giri%2C%20she%20will%20she%20will%20stay%20in%20the%20Kumbh%20tent%20city%20at%20the%20Niranjini%20Akhara%20camp%20till%20January%2015%2C%20before%20returning%20to%20the%20US%20to%20attend%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony%20of%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20January%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20first%20Amrit%20Snan%20or%20sacred%20dip%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20at%20least%203-4%20crore%20people%20will%20take%20a%20holy%20dip%20at%20the%20Triveini%20Sangam%2C%20a%20confluence%20point%20of%20the%20Ganga%2C%20Yamuna%20and%20mystical%20Saraswati%20rivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadhus%20of%20the%2013%20Akhadas%20of%20the%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20took%20a%20holy%20dip%20at%20the%20Triveni%20Sangam%20one%20by%20one.%20The%2013%20akhadas%20are%20divided%20into%20three%20groups%20--%20Sanyasi%20(Shaivite)%2C%20Bairagi%20(Vaishnav)%20and%20Udaseen.%20The%20Shaivite%20akhadas%20include%20Shree%20Panch%20Dashnam%20Juna%20Akhada%2C%20Shree%20Panchayati%20Akhada%20Niranjani%2C%20Shree%20Shambhu%20Panchayati%20Atal%20Akhada%2C%20Shree%20Panchayati%20Akhada%20Mahanirvani%2C%20Shree%20Shambhu%20Panchagni%20Akhada%2C%20Shree%20Panchdashnam%20Aavahan%20Akhada%20and%20Taponidhi%20Shri%20Anand%20Akhada%20Panchayti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaha%20Kumbh%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20significant%20religious%20congregations%20in%20the%20world%2C%20held%20every%2012%20years%20at%20one%20of%20four%20locations%20in%20India.%20The%20Maha%20Kumbh%202