com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ffake-findings-at-1-am-trump-on-jake-smith-jan-6-investigation-report%2Farticleshow%2F117227637.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ffake-findings-at-1-am-trump-on-jake-smith-jan-6-investigation-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F117227637.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ffake-findings-at-1-am-trump-on-jake-smith-jan-6-investigation-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F117227637.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Rekha%20revealed%20Big%20B's%20bizarre%20James%20Dean%20story%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736840658000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117228450%2Cimgsize-44212.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Frekha-reveals-amitabh-bachchans-bizarre-james-dean-story-that-saved-her-during-a-crucial-scene-in-silsila%2Farticleshow%2F117228471.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F117228471.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERekha%20shared%20how%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20helped%20her%20calm%20nerves%20during%20a%20challenging%20scene%20in%20Silsila%20by%20telling%20her%20a%20story%20about%20James%20Dean.%20Despite%20the%20pressure%20and%20large%20crowd%2C%20her%20performance%20was%20flawless%2C%20highlighting%20the%20strong%20on-screen%20chemistry%20between%20Rekha%20and%20Amitabh%20that%20remains%20iconic%20in%20Bollywood.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Frekha-reveals-amitabh-bachchans-bizarre-james-dean-story-that-saved-her-during-a-crucial-scene-in-silsila%2Farticleshow%2F117228471.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Guilt%20Of%20Asking%20For%20Leave%20-%20Indians%20On%2090-Hour%20Workweek%20And%20Toxic%20Bosses%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESwati%20Bose%20was%20ecstatic.%20After%20nailing%20a%20rigorous%20interview%20process%2C%20she%20landed%20a%20role%20in%20a%20digital%20marketing%20company.%20The%20first%20day%20was%20filled%20with%20smiles%2C%20introductions%2C%20and%20the%20promise%20of%20growth.%20But%20what%20began%20as%20a%20warm%20welcome%20quickly%20devolved%20into%20chaos%20-%20all%20it%20took%20was%20five%20days.%20Within%20five%20days%2C%20her%20optimism%20was%20replaced%20by%20toxicity%20at%20the%20workplace%2C%20tears%2C%20and%20ultimately%2C%20resignation.%20Her%20mental%20health%20took%20a%20nosedive%2C%20spiralling%20into%20depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwati's%20story%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20is%20far%20from%20unique.%20While%20she%20survived%2C%20some%20have%20suffered%20worse%20due%20to%20work-related%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnna%20Sebastian%20Perayil%2C%20an%20Ernst%20%26amp%3B%20Young%20(EY)%20employee%2C%20allegedly%20died%20of%20stress%20four%20months%20after%20joining%20the%20company%20last%20year.%20Anna's%20mother%2C%20Anita%20Augustine%2C%20wrote%20to%20Ernst%20%26amp%3B%20Young%20India%20Chairman%20Rajiv%20Memani%20and%20flagged%20a%20culture%20that%20%26quot%3Bseems%20to%20glorify%20overwork%20while%20neglecting%20the%20very%20human%20being%20behind%20the%20role%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20industries%2C%20employees%20are%20battling%20toxic%20workplace%20environments%20that%20prioritise%20profits%20and%20performance%20over%20mental%20well-being.%20The%20recent%20remarks%20by%20SN%20Subrahmanyan%2C%20Chairman%20of%20L%26amp%3BT%2C%20have%20triggered%20debates%20about%20workplace%20culture%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20overworking.%20In%20a%20widely%20circulated%20video%2C%20Mr%20Subrahmanyan%20suggested%20that%20employees%20should%20work%2090%20hours%20per%20week%2C%20including%20weekends%2C%20to%20stay%20competitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Feed%20The%20Mule'%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notion%20of%20a%2090-hour%20workweek%2C%20as%20suggested%20by%20Mr%20Subrahmanyan%2C%20harkens%20back%20to%20the%20coal-mining%20era%20when%20long%20hours%20spent%20inside%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20ground%20and%20covering%20both%20your%20face%20and%20lugs%20with%20coal%20dust%20were%20seen%20as%20a%20badge%20of%20honour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20it's%20a%20four-day%20workweek%20or%20a%20seven-day%20workweek%2C%2010-plus%20hours%20per%20day%20is%20not%20commendable%20at%20all.%20It%20is%20unhealthy%2C%20unsustainable%2C%20and%20ultimately%20counterproductive%2C%26quot%3B%20Niharika%20Rao%2C%20a%2026-year-old%20techie%2C%20who%20quit%20her%20job%20at%20a%20global%20firm%20recently%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Subrahmanyan%20is%20not%20the%20only%20industry%20giant%20who%20subscribes%20to%20that%20school%20of%20thought.%20Infosys%20boss%20Narayana%20Murthy%2C%20Tesla%20Chief%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20Ola%20CEO%20Bhavish%20Aggarwal%20and%20even%20Ratan%20Tata%20at%20one%20point%20or%20the%20other%20have%20advocated%20for%20longer%20working%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20average%20IT%20guy%20has%20a%20productive%20attention%20span%20of%202%20hours%20out%20of%20the%20designated%208.%20Making%20him%20work%2014%20hours%20will%20reduce%20it%20to%201%20hour.%20Making%20a%20mule%20carry%20a%20truckload%20of%20chickpeas%20won't%20convert%20it%20into%20a%20horse%3B%20feeding%20it%20might%20have%20a%20chance%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tushar%20Mohanty%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20senior%20data%20scientist%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20many%20surveys%2C%20an%20overwhelming%20number%20of%20Indian%20employees%20report%20experiencing%20workplace%20stress.%20A%20statistic%20from%20the%20Gallup%20Global%20Workplace%20Report%202024%20reveals%20that%2086%20per%20cent%20of%20Indian%20employees%20feel%20either%20'struggling'%20or%20'suffering'%20in%20their%20roles.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnData%20from%20the%20ADP%20Research%20Institute%20reveals%20about%2076%20per%20cent%20of%20Indian%20workers%20report%20that%20stress%20negatively%20impacts%20their%20work%20performance%2C%20while%2049%20cent%20cite%20detrimental%20effects%20on%20their%20mental%20health.%20Globally%2C%2065%20cent%20of%20employees%20echo%20similar%20sentiments%20about%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20study%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20revealed%20that%20nearly%20one%20in%20four%20Indian%20employees%20suffer%20from%20work-related%20stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20countries%20that%20work%20fewer%20hours%20but%20achieve%20better%20results%20because%20their%20employees%20are%20well-rested.%20When%20employees%20are%20healthier%2C%20both%20cognitively%20and%20physically%2C%20their%20productivity%20increases.%20Corporates%20have%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20reshape%20their%20policies%20as%20younger%20generations%20demand%20better%20work-life%20balance%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shreya%20Kaul%2C%20a%20mental%20health%20counsellor%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnResearch%20consistently%20debunks%20the%20myth%20that%20longer%20hours%20lead%20to%20higher%20productivity.%20In%20fact%2C%20overwork%20often%20results%20in%20burnout%2C%20reduced%20efficiency%2C%20and%20a%20host%20of%20physical%20and%20mental%20health%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProductivity%20comes%20from%20motivation%20and%20interest%20in%20the%20work%2C%20not%20from%20sheer%20hours%20spent.%20Each%20individual%20has%20unique%20drivers%2C%20and%20forcing%20long%20hours%20on%20them%20often%20strips%20away%20that%20zeal%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Rao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20every%20workplace%20I%20have%20been%20in%2C%20there%20has%20been%20some%20form%20of%20toxicity-whether%20sexism%2C%20favouritism%2C%20or%20other%20issues.%20It%20becomes%20a%20bigger%20problem%20when%20toxic%20behaviour%20comes%20from%20senior%20management%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGenerational%20Divide%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Rao%20recounted%20how%20certain%20senior%20leaders%20fostered%20an%20environment%20of%20fear%20and%20favouritism%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20employees%20to%20perform%20without%20anxiety.%20When%20asked%20if%20her%20former%20workplace%20provided%20adequate%20support%20for%20mental%20health%20challenges%2C%20she%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BNo%2C%20not%20at%20all.%20Many%20companies%20might%20offer%20a%20monthly%20mental%20well-being%20day%20off%2C%20but%20it's%20mostly%20performative.%20Genuine%20awareness%20and%20support%20for%20mental%20health%20are%20sorely%20lacking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20client%20environments%2C%20stakeholders%20and%20senior%20leadership%20treat%20you%20as%20cattle%20fodder.%20Humans%20are%20dispensable%20resources%20for%20them%20-%20make%20them%20work%20on%20weekends%2C%20public%20holidays%2C%20extended%20hours%20but%20bill%20them%20for%20only%208.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20they%20keep%20all%20the%20profits.%20Verbal%20abuse%20in%20group%20meetings%20has%20become%20normalised%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mohanty%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Rao%20also%20shed%20light%20on%20age-based%20discrimination%2C%20a%20subtle%20but%20pervasive%20issue%20in%20many%20workplaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20often%20passive-aggressive.%20Older%20colleagues%20sometimes%20make%20dismissive%20comments%2C%20like%2C%20'You%20don't%20know%20enough%20because%20you%20haven't%20been%20around%20as%20long%20as%20we%20have.'%20They%20disregard%20my%20opinions%20and%20undervalue%20my%20contributions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20generational%20divide%20often%20becomes%20even%20more%20pronounced%20during%20interactions%20with%20senior%20colleagues.%20According%20to%20many%20young%20workers%2C%20%C2%A0senior%20leaders'%20resistance%20to%20new%20ideas%20often%20stifles%20innovation%20and%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20age%20gap%20often%20plays%20a%20role.%20Colleagues%20who%20are%20closer%20to%20my%20age%20are%20more%20open%20to%20new%20ideas%2C%20but%20those%2010-15%20years%20older%20tend%20to%20be%20dismissive.%20It's%20especially%20challenging%20when%20these%20individuals%20are%20in%20senior%20management%20roles%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Rao%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMillennials%20and%20Gen%20Z%2C%20who%20now%20form%20a%20major%20portion%20of%20the%20workforce%2C%20prioritise%20work-life%20balance%20and%20mental%20well-being%20over%20the%20traditional%20%26quot%3Bhustle%20culture.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20older%20generations%20were%20taught%20that%20hard%20work%20equates%20to%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Kaul%20explained.%20%26quot%3BThis%20cultural%20mindset%20glorifies%20overwork%20-'jitna%20ghisengey%20utna%20better%20lagega%20logon%20ko'%20(the%20more%20you%20grind%2C%20the%20better%20you'll%20be%20perceived).%20But%20younger%20generations%20are%20challenging%20this%20narrative%2C%20advocating%20for%20balance%20and%20mental%20health.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Rao%20recounted%20a%20recent%20incident%20where%20her%20efforts%20to%20foster%20a%20healthy%20work-life%20balance%20for%20her%20team%20clashed%20with%20her%20senior%20manager's%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20senior%20staff%20wanted%20me%20to%20adopt%20toxic%20behaviours%20towards%20my%20team%2C%20like%20micromanaging%20and%20overloading%20them%20with%20work.%20When%20I%20refused%2C%20I%20was%20threatened%20with%20replacement.%20I%20was%20even%20told%20my%20appraisal%20and%20promotion%20could%20be%20affected.%20Feedback%20is%20now%20a%20minefield%20I'd%20rather%20avoid%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGen%20Z%20professionals%20often%20feel%20immense%20pressure%20to%20prove%20themselves.%20This%20often%20leads%20to%20overwork%20and%2C%20eventually%2C%20burnout.%20Organisations%20can%20address%20this%20by%20providing%20clearer%20growth%20paths%2C%20mental%20health%20support%2C%20and%20flexible%20work%20arrangements.%20Simple%20measures%20like%20team%20outings%20and%20informal%20interactions%20can%20also%20help%20younger%20employees%20decompress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompanies%20should%20regularly%20check%20in%20on%20employees%2C%20not%20just%20about%20work%20but%20about%20how%20we're%20feeling%20mentally.%20Providing%20access%20to%20counselling%20services%20and%20creating%20a%20supportive%20environment%20where%20employees%20can%20openly%20discuss%20stress%20would%20help%20immensely%2C%26quot%3B%20Noopur%20Goyal%2C%20a%2024-year-old%20Public%20Relations%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStress%2C%20Then%20Guilt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManaging%20stress%20in%20such%20a%20hostile%20environment%20is%20a%20tall%20task.%20Some%20face%20guilt%20for%20taking%20time%20off%20while%20some%20feel%20taking%20vacations%20or%20personal%20time%20off%20would%20send%20the%20wrong%20message%20to%20bosses%20who%20they%20think%20would%20perceive%20them%20as%20%26quot%3Bunprofessional%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20found%20solace%20in%20forming%20small%20support%20groups%20with%20colleagues%20who%20share%20similar%20struggles.%20We%20vent%2C%20share%20our%20experiences%2C%20and%20leave%20office%20trauma%20behind%20before%20heading%20home.%20It's%20been%20incredibly%20therapeutic%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Rao%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20like%20a%20crime%20to%20ask%20for%20leave%20because%20there's%20no%20one%20to%20take%20on%20my%20responsibilities.%20My%20team%20often%20bears%20the%20brunt%20of%20my%20absence%2C%20which%20only%20adds%20to%20my%20guilt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20a%20country%20of%20over%201.4%20billion.%20Unemployment%20coupled%20with%20a%20lack%20of%20opportunities%20means%20no%20one%20is%20indispensable.%20Resign%20and%20there%20are%20thousands%20if%20not%20lakhs%20to%20replace%20you%20in%20a%20second.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%2C%20as%20a%20country%20and%20culture%2C%20has%20generally%20always%20been%20very%20end%20result-oriented.%20We%20tend%20to%20prioritise%20results%20over%20the%20process.%20This%20consequence-driven%20mindset%20often%20leads%20to%20many%20misassumptions%2C%26quot%3B%20explained%20Ms%20Kaul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20safety%20measures%20and%20inadequate%20handling%20of%20harassment%20complaints%20are%20often%20recurring%20themes%20in%20employees'%20lives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20office%20has%20someone%20whose%20behaviour%20makes%20you%20feel%20like%20you're%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20resigning%20or%20losing%20your%20job.%20It's%20exhausting%20and%20deeply%20unsettling.%20My%20first%20company%20had%20some%20measures%20in%20place%2C%20but%20most%20others%20have%20been%20woefully%20inadequate%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Rao%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20companies%20scheduling%20countless%20workplace%20sensitisation%20or%20Prevention%20of%20Sexual%20Harassment%20(POSH)%20training%20sessions%2C%20the%20question%20still%20remains%3A%20Are%20we%20doing%20enough%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E(Names%20of%20workers%20have%20been%20changed%20to%20protect%20their%20identities)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736840460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fnqqu05s8_work-stress-_625x300_14_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fl-t-chairman-sn-subrahmanyan-narayana-murthy-ndtv-special-90-hour-workweek-with-gen-z-divide-whats-poisoning-indian-offices-7469954%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20recent%20remarks%20by%20SN%20Subrahmanyan%2C%20Chairman%20of%20L%26amp%3BT%2C%20have%20triggered%20debates%20about%20workplace%20culture%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20overworking.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%