pg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2Fvermicompost-kavya-4-1736391970-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-396829%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhen%20Kavya%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20quit%20her%20government%20job%20bewildered%20her%20family%2C%20her%20husband%20became%20her%20pillar%20of%20strength%2C%20she%20says.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarsha%20Markad%2C%20who%20took%20training%20from%20Kavya%20last%20January%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CUnder%20Kavya%E2%80%99s%20guidance%2C%20I%20gained%20hands-on%20experience%20after%20our%20initial%20theoretical%20lessons.%20She%20showed%20me%20the%20practical%20aspects%20of%20setting%20up%20compost%20beds%20and%20the%20entire%20process%20of%20transforming%20dung%20into%20compost%2C%20which%20was%20incredibly%20beneficial.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20knowledge%20enabled%20her%20to%20establish%20a%20vermicompost%20unit.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20care%20for%20200%20bovines%2C%20providing%20them%20shelter%2C%20and%20utilise%20their%20dung%20for%20producing%20vermicompost.%20This%20not%20only%20helps%20us%20cover%20the%20costs%20of%20maintaining%20the%20cowshed%20but%20also%20generates%20profit.%20Just%20two%20weeks%20after%20completing%20my%20training%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20launch%20our%20unit%2C%20and%20now%2C%20I%20sell%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F329041%2Fassam-woman-starts-vermicompost-business-after-husband-death-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20fertiliser%20%3C%2Fa%3Edirectly%20to%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhushal%20Singh%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20non-profit%20for%20tree%20conservation%2C%20also%20undertook%20training%20from%20Kavya%20to%20learn%20the%20nitty%20gritty%20of%20vermicomposting.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20to%20buy%20vermicompost%20from%20