%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAligned%20with%20eight%20UN%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%2C%20the%20kenaf%20fibre-based%20pads%20also%20offer%20a%20climate-friendly%20solution.%20Niveda%20highlights%20that%20their%20products%20%E2%80%9Cemit%20143%20times%20less%20carbon%20compared%20to%20traditional%20options%2C%E2%80%9D%20contributing%20to%20reduced%20air%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20truly%20test%20their%20sustainability%20claim%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20conduct%20a%20little%20experiment%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Meena.%20%E2%80%9CI%20buried%20a%20used%20Bliss%20pad%20to%20see%20if%20it%20would%20actually%20biodegrade.%20I%20was%20thrilled%20to%20find%20that%20it%20had%20completely%20decomposed%20within%20a%20few%20months%2C%20leaving%20no%20trace%20behind.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBliss%20Natural%20backs%20its%20bio-based%20claim%20with%20certifications%20from%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Indian%20Standards%20(BIS)%2C%20a%20crucial%20requirement%20for%20selling%20sanitary%20napkins.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20have%20undergone%20a%20Lifecycle%20Assessment%20Test%20(LCA)%20to%20analyse%20the%20product%E2%80%99s%20environmental%20impact%20from%20raw%20material%20to%20finished%20product.%20They%20have%20also%20received%20certifications%20from%20the%20US%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20(FDA)%20and%20the%20Central%20Drug%20Standard%20Control%20Organization%20(CDSCO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Bliss%20Natural%20promises%20to%20donate%20one%20pad%20to%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20rural%20area%20for%20every%2010%20pads%20sold.%20%3Cem%3EVaram%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20fundraising%20event%20established%20by%20Bliss%20Naturals%2C%20helped%20raise%203.5%20lakh%20pads%20and%20donated%20more%20than%2010%20lakh%20pads%20to%20women%20who%20cannot%20afford%20the%20economic%20burden.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20fundraising%20has%20paused%2C%20the%20organisation%20continues%20to%20provide%20sanitary%20napkins%20to%20women%20through%20outreach%20programmes%