d%20no%20right%20whatsoever%20to%20destroy%20what%20I%20could%20not%20create.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETapping%20on%20this%20sentiment%2C%20he%20gravitated%20to%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20spectrum%20%E2%80%94%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnknowst%20to%20many%2C%20this%20spur-of-the-moment%20decision%20went%20on%20to%20have%20an%20outsized%20impact%20on%20the%20future%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20wildlife%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20life%20dedicated%20to%20the%20tigers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20poignancy%20of%20the%20moment%2C%20Brinda%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20he%20%5BBilly%20Arjan%5D%20shot%20the%20leopard%2C%20he%20saw%20the%20light%20in%20its%20eyes%20go%20out.%20That%20was%20the%20moment%20he%20was%20converted.%20He%20realised%20it%20was%20a%20dreadful%20thing%20to%20do%3B%20a%20cruel%20sport.%20He%20became%20extremely%20sorrowful%2C%20almost%20like%20an%20epiphany.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20he%20became%20a%20conservationist.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20buzzword%20today%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360895%2Fvivek-menon-wildlife-trust-of-india-wildlife-conservation-anti-poaching-elephant-corridors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20conservation%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewasn%E2%80%99t%20understood%20as%20well%20in%20the%201960s.%20But%20Billy%20Arjan%20led%20the%20revolution%20on%20a%20piece%20of%20land%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20came%20to%20be%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Tiger%20Haven%E2%80%99%2C%20standing%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20present-day%20Dudhwa%20Tiger%20Reserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5