%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fphoto%252F%253Ffbid%253D456683486504283%2526set%253Da.456683459837619%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22533%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20glint%20of%20the%20awards%20pales%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20satisfaction%20that%20Billy%20Arjan%20had%20each%20time%20a%20tiger%20lived%20because%20of%20his%20efforts.%20Today%2C%20the%20landscape%20of%20Dudhwa%20National%20Park%20%E2%80%94%20a%20490%20sq%20km%20park%20established%20in%201977%2C%20which%20connects%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F223054%2Fkerala-forest-department-tiger-sreenivasan-earth-hero-india-say143%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimportant%20tiger%20habitats%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20India%20and%20Nepal%20%E2%80%94%20is%20decorated%20with%20elephants%2C%20rhinos%2C%20over%2045%20species%20of%20birds%20and%20of%20course%2C%20tigers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommending%20his%20passion%2C%20Brinda%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20family%20always%20knew%20him%20as%20a%20person%20of%20tremendous%20belief.%20We%20were%20always%20proud%20of%20him.%E2%80%9D%20Brinda%20is%20at%20the%20helm%20of%20affairs%20at%20Tiger%20Haven%20Society%2C%20which%20continues%20to%20champion%20Billy%20Arjan%E2%80%99s%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20his%20life%2C%20why%20anyone%20would%20want%20to%20hunt%20down%20an%20animal%20that%20is%20the%20core%20of%20the%20ecosystem%20was%20an%20enigma%20to%20him.%20And%2C%20till%20his%20last%20breath%2C%20he%20maintained%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20air%20we%20breathe%20and%20the%20water%20we%20drink%20stem%20from%20the%20biodiversity%20of%20the%20universal%20environment%20and%20its%20economics.%20The%20tiger%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20this%20truth.%20If%20it%20goes%2C%20we%20go.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESpecial%20thanks%20to%20Amith%20Bangre%2C%20General%20Manager%20and%20Chief%20Natura